<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="as-dry-as-dust">(as) dry as dust</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>枯燥无味的；渴死人的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“You’re a very silly person,” the figure in the doorway said, his voice dry as dust.
“你真是个蠢人！”门口那人说，声音干巴巴的。</p><footer>2006 江西</footer></div></div>